A long time ago, There's a machine in the
heavens called the destiny Astrolabe, that

00:00:14.159 --> 00:00:17.099
is capable of controlling the fates of mortals.

00:00:17.099 --> 00:00:21.820
When the goddess Nwa saved the world by sealing
the sky with a sacred stone, a Giant was also

00:00:21.820 --> 00:00:23.090
born from it's remainders.

00:00:23.090 --> 00:00:28.030
The monster refused to accept his fate, and
fought against the heavens in order to destroy

00:00:28.030 --> 00:00:29.749
the destiny astrolabe.

00:00:29.749 --> 00:00:34.560
The celestial armies were able to defeat the
giant and scatter his body across the land,

00:00:34.560 --> 00:00:39.630
where eventually it became the flower mountain
and the heart stone gave life to the monkey demon.

00:00:39.630 --> 00:00:44.550
However, the Destiny Astrolabe summons a series
of disasters that left the flower mountain

00:00:44.550 --> 00:00:49.010
in ruins, and the monkey demon swears to take
vengeance on the heavens.

00:00:49.010 --> 00:00:53.720
The main character WuKong arrives at the immortal's
academy, where the head master will select

00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:57.670
individuals worthy of entering the heaven
and becoming immortal.

00:00:57.670 --> 00:01:02.370
Instead of attending the ceremony, he steals
food from the kitchen, which causes the captain

00:01:02.370 --> 00:01:05.330
of the guards to not receives his food
from the server.

00:01:05.330 --> 00:01:09.290
The man bullies the girl and escalates the
situation to where he attacks her with his

00:01:09.290 --> 00:01:14.990
weapon, but luckily, a recent graduate, Juanlian,
protects her from the devastating hit.

00:01:14.990 --> 00:01:19.210
This only makes the soldier angrier, and Juanlian
gets knocked across the room.

00:01:19.210 --> 00:01:23.940
However, the captain gets kicked by another
Deity named AhZi, and she embarrasses him

00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:25.210
in front of the crowd.

00:01:25.210 --> 00:01:29.250
The man becomes furious and sends the guards
to attack the girl, but they are quickly tossed

00:01:29.250 --> 00:01:33.780
aside by Wukong, who grabs onto the captain
and kicks him through the tables.

00:01:33.780 --> 00:01:38.010
Numerous guards arrive into the room and surrounds
Wukong, but he summons his weapon from his

00:01:38.010 --> 00:01:41.040
ear, which turns into a staff that's made
from lava.

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:45.380
The soldiers charge at the man, but he summons
the flames from the weapon, which causes a

00:01:45.380 --> 00:01:48.710
huge explosion that sends the enemies flying
backwards.

00:01:48.710 --> 00:01:53.680
General Hua of the celestial army is notified
of the fight in the ceremony, and sends her

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:57.290
right hand man Tien to resolve the situation.

00:01:57.290 --> 00:02:01.450
Wukong looks at the soldiers lying on the
floor and smirks in satisfaction, but quickly

00:02:01.450 --> 00:02:06.900
senses the incoming danger as Tien flys in
to attack him with numerous daggers.

00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:10.599
Wukong is able to counter the strikes, but
the numerous blades make it difficult for

00:02:10.599 --> 00:02:12.439
him to land any direct hit.

00:02:12.439 --> 00:02:18.010
The blade master sends numerous daggers towards
Wukong that turns into a giant tornado, surrounding

00:02:18.010 --> 00:02:20.069
him in a twister of blades.

00:02:20.069 --> 00:02:24.590
After being cornered with no way out, Wukong
slams the staff onto the floor, and it begins

00:02:24.590 --> 00:02:28.269
growing to an incredible size that eventually
hits the ceiling.

00:02:28.269 --> 00:02:32.969
He kicks the massive weapon as it drops towards
Tien, breaking open the flying blades.

00:02:32.969 --> 00:02:37.989
The blade master dodges the attack, but Wukong
grabs the staff and hurls it at the opponent,

00:02:37.989 --> 00:02:39.939
Forcing Tien to leap into the air.

00:02:39.939 --> 00:02:45.239
AhZi tells them to stop, but WUkong is unable
to withdraw his attack that's heading her way.

00:02:45.239 --> 00:02:49.319
The weapon slams into the girl, but she appears
to have stopped it with one finger.

00:02:49.319 --> 00:02:53.730
However, it turns out that another man stopped
the attack using one hand while trying to

00:02:53.730 --> 00:02:56.800
protect the girl, and he calls himself Erlang.

00:02:56.800 --> 00:03:01.359
The man reveals his right arm that's imbued
with godly powers and punches the giant staff

00:03:01.359 --> 00:03:05.010
towards Wukong, which breaks the weapon as
it flys backwards.

00:03:05.010 --> 00:03:09.129
Wukong retracts the staff and leaps into the
air, planning to destroy his opponent with

00:03:09.129 --> 00:03:10.239
a final attack,

00:03:10.239 --> 00:03:14.620
but Erlang charges towards the man and proceeds
to land a devastating punch that throws the

00:03:14.620 --> 00:03:18.139
main character into the walls, knocking him
out in the process.

00:03:18.139 --> 00:03:22.310
The guards are able to capture Wukong and
lock him into the cells, while the head master

00:03:22.310 --> 00:03:26.280
apologizes profusely towards General Hua for
the incident.

00:03:26.280 --> 00:03:31.059
AhZi arrives as well and begins complaining
about why his friend Erlang was also imprisoned

00:03:31.059 --> 00:03:34.519
alongside Wukong, since all he did was stop
the fight.

00:03:34.519 --> 00:03:38.980
The general explains that Erlang disobeyed
her orders by fighting, when she only commanded

00:03:38.980 --> 00:03:40.650
Tien to resolve the situation.

00:03:40.650 --> 00:03:45.019
It turns out that AhZi is the daughter of
the general, but their relationship is clearly

00:03:45.019 --> 00:03:50.059
strained as the girl dislikes her mother's
habit of imposing her will onto everyone.

00:03:50.059 --> 00:03:54.489
At the same time, the two men are locked into
the same prison, and Wukong complains about

00:03:54.489 --> 00:03:57.799
how their previous fight was unfair since
it was two on one.

00:03:57.799 --> 00:04:02.689
He demands to fight Erlang again, but when
the man refuses, Wukong begins insulting Erlang's

00:04:02.689 --> 00:04:06.189
mother who was punished by the general for
loving a mortal.

00:04:06.189 --> 00:04:10.419
This infuriates the man, and just before they
start fighting again, the general arrives

00:04:10.419 --> 00:04:12.739
to the prison accompanied by Tien.

00:04:12.739 --> 00:04:16.989
She unchains Erlang and tells him to wait
for her in the council, while Wukong continues

00:04:16.989 --> 00:04:19.840
to complain about why his rival was set free.

00:04:19.840 --> 00:04:24.060
The general takes out the crown of binding
and puts it on the head of the prisoner.

00:04:24.060 --> 00:04:28.550
She begins chanting and the crown shrinks,
causing immense pain to Wukong as he screams

00:04:28.550 --> 00:04:31.530
on the floor, eventually fainting to the pressure.

00:04:31.530 --> 00:04:35.650
She give her daughter the scepter capable
of controlling the crown and tells AhZi to

00:04:35.650 --> 00:04:38.909
keep the man under supervision at all times.

00:04:38.909 --> 00:04:42.560
Wukong begins dreaming about his past, and
it turns out that he was the demon monkey

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:44.060
created by the heart stone.

00:04:44.060 --> 00:04:49.100
A deity took pity on him and saved him from
dying, but also sealing his powers inside

00:04:49.100 --> 00:04:52.640
the human form in order to save him from the
wrath of gods.

00:04:52.640 --> 00:04:57.379
At the same time, General Hua lectures Erlang
about his unwillingness to let go of human

00:04:57.379 --> 00:05:02.699
emotions, which prevents him from opening
his third eye that would grant him immense powers

00:05:02.699 --> 00:05:08.009
She tells him to forget about his mother and
Ahzi, so that he may become a true deity.

00:05:08.009 --> 00:05:12.770
Wukong wakes up finding himself with Ahzi,
and swears that he'll regain freedom by removing

00:05:12.770 --> 00:05:13.770
the bindings.

00:05:13.770 --> 00:05:18.180
He screams at her in anger, but when Azhi
takes out the scepter, Wukong quickly bows

00:05:18.180 --> 00:05:22.110
down to the girl, trying to avoid the pain
that he experienced before.

00:05:22.110 --> 00:05:26.330
He goes to a seminar where the headmaster
is showing the students how the heaven works.

00:05:26.330 --> 00:05:30.520
They cross the bridge that separates the realm
from the mortals, which the man claims would

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:33.740
take away their powers once they fall into
the waters.

00:05:33.740 --> 00:05:38.190
The room eventually leads to the Destiny Astrolabe,
where all mortal affairs are controlled by

00:05:38.190 --> 00:05:39.449
the machine.

00:05:39.449 --> 00:05:43.500
General Hua begins lecturing the crowd abut
the history of the heaven, and purposely speaks

00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:47.810
about the annihilation of flower mountain
in order to test Wukong's true objective for

00:05:47.810 --> 00:05:48.830
being here.

00:05:48.830 --> 00:05:53.210
the monkey demon becomes furious at hearing
the woman's compassionless rant, but before

00:05:53.210 --> 00:05:58.789
he can do anything hasty, AhZi interrupt her
mother and publicly disagrees with her ideals.

00:05:58.789 --> 00:06:03.199
She argues that heaven is supposed to represent
justice, and questions how destroying someone's

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:05.470
home can represent such ideal?

00:06:05.470 --> 00:06:09.250
The general states that everything is done
according to the Destiny Astrolabe, which

00:06:09.250 --> 00:06:11.400
is the ultimate justice.

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:16.039
After purposely enraging the monkey demon,
general Hua confirms that the demon who attacked

00:06:16.039 --> 00:06:21.189
the heavens before still lives on inside Wukong,
and orders Tien to retrieve the heart stone

00:06:21.189 --> 00:06:22.729
by killing him.

00:06:22.729 --> 00:06:26.659
Wukong manages to trick Juanlian and knocks
him out while taking his key that opens the

00:06:26.659 --> 00:06:28.390
gates to the councils.

00:06:28.390 --> 00:06:32.330
He jumps on the bridge of destiny, planning
to destroy the astrolabe, freeing all the

00:06:32.330 --> 00:06:36.840
mortals from their predestined fates, but
Erlang stops him from his attacks and warns

00:06:36.840 --> 00:06:38.389
him about breaking the laws

