the man takes out his sword and charges at
the monkey demon, stabbing the the staff and

00:06:42.409 --> 00:06:44.370
freezing it's fire elements.

00:06:44.370 --> 00:06:48.840
He throws Wukong on the floor, and continues
to strike him with a fury of slashes, but

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:51.240
the demon manages to dodge all the attacks.

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:55.660
Their fight begins to damage the bridge itself
which causes a storm to arise.

00:06:55.660 --> 00:07:00.099
AhZi realizes that something is wrong, when
she finds Juanlian unconscious in the kitchen

00:07:00.099 --> 00:07:01.300
with the keys missing.

