00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:15.331
AhZi arrives at the bridge with Juanlian,
and tries to tell them to stop, but Wukong

00:07:15.331 --> 00:07:21.150
strikes the floor and enlarges the staff after
being cornered, which destroys the structure completely.

00:07:21.150 --> 00:07:26.289
The group falls from the sky alongside the
giant weapon and crashes into the land of the mortals

00:07:26.289 --> 00:07:30.569
The group survives the fall, and questions
their location, but Tien realizes that they

00:07:30.569 --> 00:07:33.400
have landed on what used to be the flower
mountain.

00:07:33.400 --> 00:07:37.490
The three man continues to fight each other,
but soon realizes that their powers are gone

00:07:37.490 --> 00:07:39.930
after entering through the bridge of destiny.

00:07:39.930 --> 00:07:44.169
Their fights are cut short when a large cloud
begins to form on top of the village, and

00:07:44.169 --> 00:07:47.860
the villagers rush into the building in fear
of the demon that is about to wreak havoc

00:07:47.860 --> 00:07:49.090
on the town.

00:07:49.090 --> 00:07:53.240
The cloud monster begins taking the people
as it steals the water from the humans.

00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:58.470
Tien sees a child outside and to his surprise,
a woman runs to protect the boy from danger

00:07:58.470 --> 00:08:03.840
He rushes to save them and carries them inside,
but gets held on by the cloud demon and pulled

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.379
towards the center.

00:08:05.379 --> 00:08:11.050
Before the man can be completely consumed,
Wukong grabs onto him alongside with everyone else.

00:08:11.050 --> 00:08:15.560
Ahzi shoots the cloud demon with an ice arrow
that Juanlian invented, freezing the monster

00:08:15.560 --> 00:08:17.340
and forcing it to retreat.

00:08:17.340 --> 00:08:22.330
The next morning, Wukong wakes up and realizes
that he's tied up by AhZi in order to prevent

00:08:22.330 --> 00:08:24.319
further fighting amongst the group.

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:28.290
She tells Wukong and Erlang that they have
to help the villagers, as the people have

00:08:28.290 --> 00:08:32.400
suffered a great deal and thinks that they
are deities sent from heaven.

00:08:32.400 --> 00:08:36.960
The two refuses at first, but after seeing
the misfortunes that the villagers are suffering

00:08:36.960 --> 00:08:41.490
from with their own eyes, they decide to capture
the cloud demon and save the people together.

00:08:41.490 --> 00:08:46.380
Tien explains that the cloud used to be from
the heavens, but wondered off and became corrupted

00:08:46.380 --> 00:08:48.710
by the demonic auras from the ruins.

00:08:48.710 --> 00:08:53.830
It took all the water from the village, therefore
causing drought and preventing any crops to grow.

00:08:53.830 --> 00:08:57.950
They plan to trick the monster and capture
it by projecting a sunset, and weaken it by

00:08:57.950 --> 00:09:00.220
firing ice bombs in a large cannon.

00:09:00.220 --> 00:09:04.390
The people put up all the red cloth that they
have in a pattern, and soon the sky begins

00:09:04.390 --> 00:09:07.080
turning black as the demon appears over the
village.

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:11.920
They began shooting ice arrows at the sky,
but that only manages to annoy the monster

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:13.370
as it retreats temporarily.

00:09:13.370 --> 00:09:18.040
Tien grabs the torch and throws it under the
field of red cloth, creating the illusion

00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:22.720
of a sunset which triggers the monster as
it begins revealing it's true form.

00:09:22.720 --> 00:09:27.140
The demon approaches closer, and Wukong takes
this opportunity to load up the cannon and

00:09:27.140 --> 00:09:29.350
fires directly at the demon's face.

00:09:29.350 --> 00:09:33.750
The monster freezes quickly and falls towards
the city where Tien capture it by trapping

00:09:33.750 --> 00:09:35.300
it within a cage.

00:09:35.300 --> 00:09:39.280
The people begin cheering as the sky finally
rains after years of drought.

00:09:39.280 --> 00:09:44.340
At night, the villagers gather together as
they celebrate the victory against the demon,

00:09:44.340 --> 00:09:48.590
but Juanlian feels something wrong as ice
particles began forming in the air.

00:09:48.590 --> 00:09:53.100
He notices a mysterious figure in the background,
who appears in front of the people with dark

00:09:53.100 --> 00:09:55.100
aura surrounding his body.

00:09:55.100 --> 00:09:59.460
