More assassins arrive in front of Tien as
he tries to run away, but gets stabbed by

00:10:10.610 --> 00:10:13.340
the numerous ice shards across his body.

00:10:13.340 --> 00:10:17.530
Wukong notices something wrong in the air
and runs towards the town center, but when

00:10:17.530 --> 00:10:21.480
