that all the people are killed.

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:24.170
Erlang arrives as well, and is shocked at
what happened.

00:10:24.170 --> 00:10:28.920
They look at Juanlian who's barely alive,
and he apologizes for not being able to save

00:10:28.920 --> 00:10:31.470
the villagers before he dies.

00:10:31.470 --> 00:10:36.041
