The men fires at the monkey demon as he gets
impaled by numerous ice bullets and falls

00:10:42.230 --> 00:10:43.230
to the ground.

00:10:43.230 --> 00:10:47.790
The general appears and tells them that their
efforts are useless in the face of destiny,

00:10:47.790 --> 00:10:52.310
as the astrolabe has decided a long time ago
that the people were meant to die.

00:10:52.310 --> 00:10:55.810
She tells them to surrender their hopes because
everything is predestined.

00:10:55.810 --> 00:11:00.340
Wukong screams in rage as the the general
knocks him out with a final attack.

00:11:00.340 --> 00:11:05.836
AhZi wakes up in a prison cell along with
Erlang, who's accepted the rulings of the heaven.

00:11:05.836 --> 00:11:10.760
He tells her that they were wrong for disobeying
destiny and trying to save the people.

00:11:10.760 --> 00:11:14.570
Wukong is imprisoned in the deepest level
where he's constantly suffering from the worst

00:11:14.570 --> 00:11:19.210
pain imaginable, but refusing to die as he
waits for AhZi's return.

00:11:19.210 --> 00:11:24.040
The girl goes to the monkey demon and Wukong
smiles after seeing her arrival.

00:11:24.040 --> 00:11:29.390
Trying to end her friend's suffering, AhZi
tells him that she despises him and that he lost everything.

00:11:29.390 --> 00:11:33.710
The flower mountain will never return and
they cannot win against destiny.

00:11:33.710 --> 00:11:39.400
Feeling heartbroken and hopeless, Wukong finally
gives up on life and slowly turns into dust,

00:11:39.400 --> 00:11:42.730
while leaving behind the heart stone and the
scarf that he carries.

00:11:42.730 --> 00:11:46.990
AhZi promises that she'll finish her friend's
mission as she drops the scarf into the flower

00:11:46.990 --> 00:11:49.980
mountain where it lands inside the village.

