Erlang brings the heart stone to the general,
and after abandoning all emotions, he opens

00:11:54.470 --> 00:11:57.830
the third eye on his forehead and receives
tremendous power.

00:11:57.830 --> 00:12:01.870
The elder Deity picks up the scarf that was
dropped from heaven, and talks with the monkey

00:12:01.870 --> 00:12:03.740
demon in purgatory.

00:12:03.740 --> 00:12:07.760
The main character thinks that he lost everything,
but the old man disagrees.

00:12:07.760 --> 00:12:12.990
Although Wukong has lost the heart stone,
it also allowed him to abandon his mortal body.

00:12:12.990 --> 00:12:18.570
He must now decide whether if he wants to
accept destiny or fight against it with his own heart.

00:12:18.570 --> 00:12:23.920
Wukong begins lifting the giant staff symbolizing
his power, and resurrecting it into flames.

