The woman constructs a metallic wall around
herself, but Wukong strikes it repeatedly

00:14:22.040 --> 00:14:25.760
with anger and eventually manages to overpower
her magic.

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:29.920
The general is forced to teleport them outside
and begins attacking wukong with numerous

00:14:29.920 --> 00:14:35.550
blades that she created, but the demon deflects
all of them easily and breaks them into pieces.

00:14:35.550 --> 00:14:40.470
Suddenly, Wukong notices that Erlang has arrived,
and gets knocked away by his attack.

00:14:40.470 --> 00:14:45.690
The man no longer feels any emotions and has
chosen to abandoned the memories of his friends.

00:14:45.690 --> 00:14:50.180
The two charges at each other and fights furiously
as they trade blows, but Erlang gains the

00:14:50.180 --> 00:14:52.880
upper hand and pushes Wukong backwards.

00:14:52.880 --> 00:14:57.140
He summons a gigantic ice weapon that strikes
Wukong, pushing him towards the mountains

00:14:57.140 --> 00:14:58.930
and crashing into the rocks.

00:14:58.930 --> 00:15:03.150
The Demon counters by launching his weapon
as well, but Erlang stops it and breaks the

00:15:03.150 --> 00:15:06.000
staff pieces by piece, until he stabs Wukong
in the stomach.

00:15:06.000 --> 00:15:09.990
The Monkey throws away their weapons and the
two proceeds to punch each other with all

00:15:09.990 --> 00:15:14.490
their might, which causes a huge explosion
that engulfs the entire area.

00:15:14.490 --> 00:15:19.110
When the dust settles, General Hua walks towards
Erlang, but notices something wrong.

00:15:19.110 --> 00:15:23.580
The man begins recalling his memories after
striking Wukong and sensing Ahzi's presence

00:15:23.580 --> 00:15:25.030
in the demon's heart.

00:15:25.030 --> 00:15:30.470
He cries as he realizes her death and opens
his eyes, refusing to let go of Ahzi's memories

00:15:30.470 --> 00:15:33.290
and be treated as a puppet for the general's
control.

00:15:33.290 --> 00:15:37.410
Seeing that Erlang has betrayed her will,
The general decides to vanquish both of them

00:15:37.410 --> 00:15:41.750
by transfroming into a gigantic titan using
the metals around her.

00:15:41.750 --> 00:15:45.890
Wukong recovers from the ground and summons
a ball of flames that turns into his weapon.

00:15:45.890 --> 00:15:49.750
He throws the staff at the giant and leaps
onto the weapon as it becomes larger.

00:15:49.750 --> 00:15:54.030
He charges towards the general, as the weapon
flys closer to the titan.

00:15:54.030 --> 00:15:57.970
Erlang begins running as well and leaps onto
the floating rocks, getting closer towards

00:15:57.970 --> 00:15:58.970
the enemy.

00:15:58.970 --> 00:16:03.360
He leaps towards the center of the giant and
prepares his final attack, while Wukong jumps

00:16:03.360 --> 00:16:06.310
under the giant staff and swings it at the
titan.

00:16:06.310 --> 00:16:10.750
Erlang punches through the center of the giant
as Wukong lands a direct hit on the head.

00:16:10.750 --> 00:16:14.750
The giant staff breaks the general in half
as it cuts through her body and turning her

00:16:14.750 --> 00:16:15.910
into dust.

00:16:15.910 --> 00:16:19.870
The two lands back into the building after
finally destroying the general and the machine

00:16:19.870 --> 00:16:20.870
of destiny.

00:16:20.870 --> 00:16:25.130
Erlang tells Wukong that Ahzi saved him this
time, but the next time they meet will be

00:16:25.130 --> 00:16:26.880
a battle to the death.

00:16:26.880 --> 00:16:30.560
Wukong turns around and accepts the challenge,
as the two go their separate ways.

00:16:30.560 --> 00:16:34.660
Erlang will become the new general of the
celestial army, while Wukong will gather all

00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:38.780
those unwilling to accept their fates, and
wage a war against the deities that will last

00:16:38.780 --> 00:16:41.150
hundreds of years.

